songs.title: Only Human
songs.lyrics:
Cause I'm only human

[Verse 1]
How do you live when there's nothing to give
When you strive for a world without soldiers?
How do you live when there's nothing to give
To a man when he lives like he's showbiz?

[Pre-Chorus]
Some little things that you need to know
Don't disown me, cause I'm only human
I traveled far, sold my last ceremony
Cause I'm only human
Come and hold me
Get to know me
Come and hold me
Get to know me
Come and hold me
Cause I'm only, cause I'm only
Cause I'm only human

[Chorus]
Are we ever gonna change our ways?
Or are you looking for a great escape?
You don't know, you live and learn
You said you don't know, hands high, take your turn
You said you don't know, you live and learn
Cause I'm only human

[Verse 2]
How do you live when there's nothing to give?
Can you lie to a saint when he knows you?
How do you live when there's nothing to give?
Do you act like you think you're supposed to?

[Pre-Chorus]

[Chorus]

Don't disown me, cause I'm only human
I traveled far, sold my last ceremony
Cause I'm only human
